title: War of the Roses: The Mispositioned Shower Head
description: Caitlin was out town and came home to find some suspicious things happening.  First, she noticed her boyfriend Logan's motorcycle had the passenger pegs down which makes her think he had a girl riding on it with him.  Then she noticed some things of hers were going missing.  THEN she also noticed the shower head was in a different position.  Are this are coincidences or is Logan up to something?
